
In order to compile the code, you will have to:

1) install ParadisEO: 
    http://paradiseo.gforge.inria.fr/
    https://gforge.inria.fr/projects/paradiseo

2) get a copy of CPT/YAHSP

3) cp install-dist.cmake install.cmake

4) edit install.cmake to suit your configuration

5) type:
    cmake .
    make

This will create a "dae" binary, to get help, type:
    ./dae -h

